'''叠氮乙烷'''（化学式 C<sub>2</sub>H<sub>5</sub>N<sub>3</sub>）是一种极易爆炸的化合物，对加热和冲击敏感。它加热到室温时就已经爆炸。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Campbell | first1 = H. C. | last2 = Rice | first2 = O. K. | title = The Explosion of Ethyl Azide | journal = Journal of the American Chemical Society | year = 1935 | volume = 57 | issue = 6 | pages = 1044–1050 | doi = 10.1021/ja01309a019 }}</ref><ref>{{ cite journal | last1 = Rice | first1 = O. K. | last2 = Campbell | first2 = H. C. | title = The Explosion of Ethyl Azide in the Presence of Diethyl Ether | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-chemical-physics_1939-08_7_8/page/700 | journal = The Journal of Chemical Physics | year = 1939 | volume = 7 | issue  = 8 | pages = 700–709 | doi = 10.1063/1.1750516 }}</ref> 当加热至分解时，它会释放有毒的[[氮氧化物|氮氧化物]]气体。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Rice | first1 = O. K. | title = The Role of Heat Conduction in Thermal Gaseous Explosions | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-chemical-physics_1940-09_8_9/page/727 | journal = The Journal of Chemical Physics | year = 1940 | volume = 8 | issue = 9 | pages = 727–733 | doi = 10.1063/1.1750808 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Costa Cabral | first1 = B. J. | last2 = Costa | first2 = M. L. | last3 = Almoster Ferreira | first3 = M. A. | title = ChemInform Abstract: Molecular Structure and Ionization Energies of Azides: An ''ab initio'' Study of Hydrazoic Acid, Methyl Azide and Ethyl Azide | journal = ChemInform | year = 2010 | volume = 24 | issue = 37 | pages = no | doi = 10.1002/chin.199337053 }}</ref>

它会刺激眼睛、呼吸系统和皮肤。

==用处==
叠氮乙烷可用于[[有机合成|合成]][[三唑|三唑]]类有机物。<ref>Mudiraj, Anwita; Geeviman, Khamushavalli; Babu, Phanithi Prakash; Reddy, A. Ram. Triazolo aspirins inhibit proliferation of C6 glioma cell lines in vitro. ''Journal of Pharmacy Research (Mohali, India)'', 2014. 8 (6): 741-750.</ref><ref>{{cite journal|journal=Angewandte Chemie International Edition|volume=56|issue=1|language=en|date=2017-01-02|pages=346–349|doi=10.1002/anie.201609715|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/anie.201609715|title=Azidoperfluoroalkanes: Synthesis and Application in Copper(I)-Catalyzed Azide-Alkyne Cycloaddition|accessdate=2021-03-09|author=Zsófia E. Blastik, Svatava Voltrová, Václav Matoušek, Bronislav Jurásek, David W. Manley, Blanka Klepetářová, Petr Beier}}</ref>

